匹兹堡是美国重要的货运枢纽。匹兹堡有一个面积为{{convert|5000|acre|km2}}的自由贸易区，与三条一级货运铁路、一条洲际高速公路相连，几公里之外便有全美第二大港口。<ref name="xian">{{cite web|url=http://www.flypittsburgh.com/Onorato_Airport_Authority_Announce_Letter_of_Intent_with_Xian_Xianyang_International_Airport_for_Air_Cargo_Development|title=Onorato, Airport Authority Announce Letter of Intent with Xian Xianyang International Airport for Air Cargo Development|publisher=Allegheny County Airport Authority|accessdate=November 20, 2011|date=November 15, 2007|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928092125/http://www.flypittsburgh.com/Onorato_Airport_Authority_Announce_Letter_of_Intent_with_Xian_Xianyang_International_Airport_for_Air_Cargo_Development|archivedate=2011年9月28日}}</ref>匹兹堡国际机场的三大货运航空公司每年货运量达4500万吨。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flypittsburgh.com/PIT_fact_sheet|title=Pittsburgh International Airport: Fact Sheet|publisher=Allegheny County Airport Authority|accessdate=July 12, 2009|date=March 25, 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090713125220/http://www.flypittsburgh.com/PIT_fact_sheet|archivedate=2009年7月13日}}</ref>三座货运航站楼共有{{convert|183000|ft2|m2|0}}的仓库，以及{{convert|450000|ft2|m2|0}}的停机坪。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pitairport.com/Worldwide_Flight_Services_Cargo_Handling_Facilities_at_PIT_Receives_TSA_Certification|title=Worldwide Flight Services Cargo Handling Facilities at PIT Receives TSA Certification|publisher=Allegheny County Airport Authority|accessdate=November 20, 2011|date=June 12, 2009|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120407030845/http://www.pitairport.com/Worldwide_Flight_Services_Cargo_Handling_Facilities_at_PIT_Receives_TSA_Certification|archivedate=2012年4月7日}}</ref>。匹兹堡国际机场是Wings物流货运航空的枢纽。<ref>{{cite
weburl=http://www.flypittsburgh.com/PIT_Chosen_By_Wings_Logistics_As_Air_Cargo_Distribution_Point}}</ref>

